snippet.title: 99floors playthrough attempt
snippet.description:
This is my gameplay of the demo version of a game called, obviously, 99floors. I've  added a link to the creator's itch page and website if you want to give the game a try yourself.
https://www.99floorsgame.com/
https://luke-p78.itch.io/
*DISCLAIMER*
There isn't any commentary until around 34 minutes in and when I pause the game around 28:11 you can skip to around 33:20 when I unpause the game and continue playing the game because nothing of value occurs between those times and otherwise you'll just be watching a black screen with the words pause on it so I recommend skipping that. sorry that the audio's a little bit choppy, I'm not too good at editing videos and stuff right now since I don't post videos often   
*DISCLAIMER OVER*

And to the creator of this game, if you're watching this video and reading through this description, thank you. I enjoyed playing this game and hope the full version of the game is just as fun.
